{"tid":1994334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新地引入平安人壽作西九站上蓋商業項目合作投資者","createTime":"2020-04-29T11:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T11:42:17.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e81a3eb37fa17bba132cf27848f151d92a2d6d7c","tid":1994334,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T11:39:16.000Z","msg":"新地引入平安人壽作西九站上蓋商業項目合作投資者<br />\n29.04.2020 18:40<br />\n<br />\n新地(<a href=\"http://00016.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00016.HK&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=76535d1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00016.HK</a>) 宣布，平安人壽將分別斥資 93.94 億元和18.79 億元，向新地和郭氏家族公司，購入西九龍高鐵站上蓋商業項目辦公大廈合共30%權益，交易完成後，新地、平安人壽及郭氏家族公司將分別持有辦公大廈的 50%、30%及 20%權益。至於項目中的零售部分將繼續由新地全資持有。<br />\n<br />\n新地主席兼董事總經理郭炳聯表示，十分歡迎平安人壽加入成為項目的策略性投資者，指兩間公司擁有相同願景，均有意將此地標項目作為長線投資。<br />\n<br />\n新地於去年以422.32億元投得西九龍高鐵站上蓋商業項目，每方呎樓面地價13345元，成交價破官地紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284220&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1284220%26csid%3D261_341&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=d6b7ab37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284220&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"5dda805cd4d4e9ae2dbeedc09eb4016d5cfd257f","tid":1994334,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"紅地"}]}